node.text: After my session with @doc.chandon yesterday I’ve had lots of time to think. Today during my workout I felt a rush of excitement and jolt of focus take over my body. I’m responsible for my life! I’m not saying that you have to go through this journey alone, but I am saying that you have to take responsibility for your choices. Sometimes we can doubt ourselves and look to others for help when all we really need is to look deep within ourselves for the answers. Sometimes we can’t find the answers because we surround ourselves with so many distractions that it becomes too noisy in our minds. Give yourself time and quiet your mind enough to listen to what you really need to hear!! Sending my love 😍

node.text: Partnered up with @halopets and @takotenrestaurant to give thanks to our Hometown heros! Just wanted our military, police, fire, and medical staff to know how much we appreciate them! Thank you again for dedicating your lives to helping others😇😇😇 Hope you enjoyed the tacos!

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Michelle Waterson on August 18, 2021. May be an image of 1 person, standing, outdoors and tree.

node.text: When @joshuagomeznm asked me to marry him he told me he would give me the world if he could! And with Araya he has! Taking the day to realize how truly blessed I am. I think about the things Josh has sacrificed for me, for his family, and for America and I am truly grateful. If you have a veteran in your life make sure you reach out to them and thank them for the sacrifices they have made, because what they did for us matters. Sending my love to all the veterans out there, and to everyone who are currently serving.

node.text: Today is World Day Against Trafficking in Persons. An estimated 24.9 million people, including children, are trafficked around the world. I am choosing to RISE UP with @ourrescue to raise awareness about this issue. I stand for children and I invite you to join me. Together we can take a bold stand against human trafficking and sexual exploitation. ourrescue.org/riseup
